WEBVTT

00:00.062 --> 00:01.605
Previously on <i>Suits...</i>

00:02.348 --> 00:03.519
Katrina Bennett.

00:03.520 --> 00:04.787
She comes in,
she takes over,

00:04.854 --> 00:06.294
She acts like everything
is her idea.

00:06.356 --> 00:08.124
This wasn't
about a job for me.

00:08.191 --> 00:10.126
It was about having a life,

00:10.193 --> 00:12.128
But I guess
you wouldn't understand that.

00:12.195 --> 00:14.797
So you're gonna punish me
by giving me to Louis?

00:14.864 --> 00:15.998
Because you and I are done.

00:16.049 --> 00:18.667
You make me want
to be a better man.

00:18.719 --> 00:20.970
I can't let you do this.

00:22.839 --> 00:25.207
I regret where we are,

00:25.258 --> 00:27.843
And I've been trying to get us
back to where we were.

00:27.894 --> 00:29.678
You're suggesting
bribing a man

00:29.730 --> 00:31.210
to get you out
of your bribery charge.

00:31.214 --> 00:35.017
"In for a penny, in for
a pound," mother always said.

00:35.068 --> 00:36.885
Ava Hessington
doesn't plead no contest.

00:36.937 --> 00:37.937
She pleads guilty.

00:38.021 --> 00:39.321
And you get
to call it a win.

00:39.389 --> 00:41.824
I can beat you, and I did.

00:41.891 --> 00:43.776
You put me
in that position again,

00:43.860 --> 00:46.362
and I'll do
whatever I have to do to win.

00:46.413 --> 00:48.748
Are you saying screw this
deal, let's kick his ass?

00:48.832 --> 00:51.534
I'm saying take the deal.
We already did.

00:51.585 --> 00:54.570
I win, you back me
for managing partner.

00:54.621 --> 00:56.238
You want
to take down Jessica.

00:56.289 --> 00:57.540
I do.

