wanna stay for your meal ♪

07:34.654 --> 07:37.639
♪ get another piece of pie
for your wife ♪

07:37.690 --> 07:41.243
♪ everybody wanna know
how it feel ♪

07:41.310 --> 07:44.813
♪ everybody wanna see
what it's like ♪

07:44.864 --> 07:47.833
♪ living in a beehive
of your mind ♪

07:47.917 --> 07:51.115
♪ me and missus
so busy, busy making money ♪

